\id TIT - Dũya Translation Project
\h Utitu
\toc1 Ubvur Uburhu aka atsɛnge Utitu
\toc2 Utitu
\toc3 Utit
\mt2 Ubvur Uburhu aka atsɛnge
\mt1 Utitu
\imt1 Utsutson ri itsi ubvur Utitu
\ip Awu Uburhu uner itser Uyesu unga atsɛnge ubvur uwurɛ ru Utitu uwɛrhi itsernga uwuruwi aka awu ru Ukirit. Abɔɔ agɛ Uburhu atsɛng ubvur ha ru Umakidoniya, ri ivangyɛ unga aka awe ru udĩ uku uzĩ Unikaforhi ru Uakaya ra amɛk aki 65 udzur ru unumkpi umbɔ aka amar Uyesu.
\ip Ri inggbaashia Uburhu ayituwe Utitu ikpũ amɛnkɛ aka amɛ̃ɛ̃ anggbaashi abika adɔsa awe ra ake, akirakɛ aka awuweke akarhãrhã nggu ikpũ amɛnkɛ abi Ukirit aka awe ra ake. Adzowe itsũwã ru Utitu ri itsi udĩkpi unga aka imesuwe ikikɔng abika adɔsa. Ri imimasha, Uburhu adzowe itsũwã ru unga ri itsi ikpũ ibibɛkyɛ iki imɛ̃ɛ̃ abika adɔsa abɛk ra ake.
\iot Abinkɛ aka awe umɔ
\io1 Utsutson ri itsi ubvur ha \ior (1.1-4)\ior*
\io1 Anggbaashi ra abika adɔsa \ior (1.5-16)\ior*
\io1 Itser iyi ikikɔng abika adɔsa \ior (2.1-15)\ior*
\io1 Imesa nu igbiir ato \ior (3.1-11)\ior*
\io1 Imimasha \ior (3.12-15)\ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Idzeku Uburhu ugãrhã Unum nu ungwɛ̃ itser Uyesu Ukiristo. Asɛng umum na adena umum ifituwe abi imangmang ru Unum aka asɛng ni ĩdarh umbɔ ahwɛng idzidzɛrhayɛ iki ikũ izĩ idɔsu Unum,
\v 2 ngge iki isei ri ifosa iyi urhɛ uwu ugbagbaa. Unum uwuruwi aka asi igbɛrangwĩ, aka abemuwa umɛn urhɛ ha na adɔrha angwɛ̃ ivang.
\v 3 Ri ivanga uku kpengkpeng Unum akũ idzidzɛrhanga adzeka ri irhirhang ri idzowe isarhe, iyiriyɛ umbɔ aka adzaa ru umum agɛ umum ĩdũwã ri itsitsu Unum uwuku ufɔrh umɛn.
\p 
\v 4 Ubvur uwurɛ uzĩ ru Utitu ungwɛ̃mum uwu idzidzɛrhe ri imangmang. Imimuta nu ididɔɔr idzeku Unum Utɛ nu Ukiristo Uyesu Uwuku Ufɔrh umɛn.
\s1 Itser Utitu ru Ukirit
\p 
\v 5 Umum ĩbɔra ungo ru Ukirit ru ungo umashuwe itseryɛ iki ibɔr nu usɛng anggbaashi ri ikikɔng abika adɔsa ru ubɛn utepa, ru nyaka umum iki itsuka ungo.
\v 6 Awu ufang unggbaashi awu unerwi aka ashia ru uvau, awe ru utsɛrha unying ukpekũ, uwuruwi angwɛ̃nga aka awe ru imangmang ru Uyesu na asi iwembɔ abi ishera amɛn use ida igũ arherhe.
\v 7 Unggbaashi ri ikikɔng abika adɔsa adzɛu aner Unum na awu ufang unga ishia ru uvau ru ubɛn unera, asi íwea uner iberi itsi use afɛ̃rhĩ igũ avɔm, asi ídzowuka itsinga ra adɛ, use uner itsoo, use uner ikponu uhwɛk.
\v 8 Nu ngge iki iwe rimi awu ufang unga awu uner uwuku uyɛi atsen, unerwi aka abemu iyiki ize, uwuku ukpɔm itsinga, uwuku urhurhika, uwuku usar na adɔɔr.
\v 9 Arherhu-Num awu idzidzɛrhe, awu ufang unga akpɔm Arherhu-Num akarhãrhã uku kpengkpeng ru nyaka umbɔ aka amesuwe. Ngge ítsu unga afituwe abɔɔ abika adɔsi imesa ha na adɛyiwe igbigba abika akpɛ̃na ngge.
\p 
\v 10 Ubinkutsu abika asoyi amɛn awu arhɛrhɛ, abi arherhe aka atãrhã nu abika arhurhɛm, undzumunga ru ukpui abi Uyahuda abika adɔsu ikpem usorhe.
\v 11 Awu ufang umbɔ atsɛrha umbɔ anukutata, ubinkutsu umbɔ asoyi amɛn aya anera arhɛrhɛ nggu imesa iyɛ iki isi imɛ̃ngge umbɔ amesuwe ri ibee iwu ru uhwɛk.
\v 12 Uko nggaa uwuku umesuwe umbɔ agɔr agɛ, <<Abi Ukarita ubɛn ivang awu abi igbɛrangwĩ, íjuɛ iyiki ibewe, abi ighɛrha abika akponi ighabin urhɛrhɛ.>>
\v 13 Ideka iyɛrɛ iwu idzidzɛrhe. Nggee, utsɛrha umbɔ akarhãrhã, ngge itsú umbɔ awuri imangmang iyi idzidzɛrhe.
\v 14 Umbɔ awuri inekukumbɔ ikpeto ra atsutson akatãrhã abi Uyahuda nu idɔsi ikpem abirabɛ aka akpɛ̃mbɔ idzidzɛrhe.
\v 15 Ra abika asar, abina kishoo awu asarsatake, bɔr ra abirabɛ aka asi isarmbɔ na ashimbɔ ri imangmang, ubin usi isarkpɔ. Idzidzɛrhe, ifɛrhkɔmbɔ iyiki ihwɛng iyiki ize nu iyiki ibewe iki ikpengge.
\v 16 Agɔr agɛ umbɔ ahwɛngmbɔ Unum, bɔr ri itsermbɔ atsɛyimbɔ unga. Umbɔ awu abin ishĩ, abika akpɛ̃ ididɔsa, asi ídɛ̃ɛ̃ atɔ̃mbɔ itser iyiki ize.
\c 2
\s1 Ubin uku uwe ufang // umbɔ amesuwe anera
\p 
\v 1 Bɔr ungo, awu ufang ungo umesuwe ubin uku uwe uku kpengkpeng ri imesa iyi idzidzɛrhe.
\v 2 Umesuwe akakũ akatsak umbɔ angwɛ̃dzɛn nggu atsimbɔ, amɛ̃ iyɛi imor, akpɔm atsimbɔ, na adɛ̃ɛ̃ aker ri imangmang, na awe ru ibibema nu ibibima akarhãrhã.
\p 
\v 3 Rimi hã, umesuwe akakũ akatsɛrh umbɔ asei iseiyɛ iki idzowe imor ru Unum, asi ínyatumbɔ inyar, use anyanga atsimbɔ adzowe ra adɛ, bɔr amesuwe abin aka aze.
\v 4 Umbɔ amesuwe akatsɛrh abika awe ru iker umbɔ abema atsakmbɔ nu angwɛ̃mbɔ,
\v 5 na awe abika akpɔm atsimbɔ na asar, abika atɔ̃ itser ra aya, abika awu ra amɛn, abika adɔsa arherhe atsakmbɔ, ngge itsú anera asi írhenumbɔ Arherhu-Num.
\p 
\v 6 Rimi hã, ufituwe awɛdzɛm umbɔ akpɔm atsimbɔ.
\v 7 Ru ubɛn ubin ukorhu ubinkpi uku idɛyiwe umbɔ itser iyiki ize. Ungwɛ̃dzɛn nu utsu amɛnngo
\v 8 nu urherhe irhɛm iyi idzidzɛrhe ri imesango anera aka asi ídɛ̃ɛ̃ acayimbɔ. Ukorha akɛrɛ ngge ítsu abika akpɛ̃ ungo ama agũ atsa ubinkutsu umbɔ asi íkpombɔ iyiki ibeweyɛ umbɔ aka irherhe ra atsimɛn.
\p 
\v 9 Umesuwe agãrhã umbɔ adɔsa arherhe ateiyambɔ ru ubɛn ubin, na atsu umbɔ agũibɛn. Niba awembɔ ru uning nggu umbɔ,
\v 10 niba avɛumbɔ ivɛu ra aya ateiyambɔ, bɔr adɛyiwe atsimbɔ ri idzidzɛrhe ra abina kishoo. Ikorhe rimi hã ngge ítsu imesa iyɛrɛ iyi Unum Uwuku Ufɔrh umɛn iwe ru izama ru ubɛn utsĩndĩã.
\p 
\v 11 Imimutu Unum iyiki ikũ ififɔrh iki idzekangge ra anera kishoo.
\v 12 Imesuwa umɛn igɛ umɛn ĩgɔr ugɛ <<Ĩ'ĩ>> ri ikpona abin upfung nu ikorha abinkɛ Unum aka asi ibemunga. Imesuwa umɛn igɛ umɛn ĩgɔr ugɛ <<Ĩĩ>> ri ibibɛk ri ikpɔm atsimɛn, iwe abika arhurhika, ni ibɛk ru nyaka Unum aka abee umɛn ibɛk ru upfung ukpu irherɛ.
\v 13 Umɛn ikorhe rimi ri idzɛu ifosa iyi Unum aka atsuke idorh, ngge iwu ibiba ikpikpoi iyi nggaa Unummɛn nu Uwuku Ufɔrh, Uyesu Ukiristo.
\v 14 Unga adzowe itsinga na afai na afɔna umɛn ri kishoo iyiki ibewemɛn na asare anerabɛ aka awu abinga, abika atsu amɛn atɔ̃ itser iyiki ize.
\p 
\v 15 Umesuwe abin akɛrɛ. Ufituwe nu utsɛrhe nggu ijee kishoo. Niba uneke unera akwɛɛrka ungo.
\c 3
\s1 Ikorhe ubin uku uze
\p 
\v 1 Uyituwe anera umbɔ adɔsa arherhe abi ijee, na agbisha adzɛu itɔ̃ ubɛn itser iyiki ize.
\v 2 Niba arherhumbɔ arherhe urhena ri itsi ubɛn unera, asei uku ughwɔɔw, awe abika adɔɔr na arhɛrhe atsimbɔ ra anera kishoo.
\p 
\v 3 Isha umɛn iwu aguge, iwemɛn ru ida idɔsa arherhe, abina akɔɔ aka arhɛm umɛn. Ni iwe agãrhã ri ikpona ru ikpũ abina arhɛrhɛ ru upfung. Ibibɛkmɛn iwu ibewe nu unyɛ̃ɛ̃, abɔɔ akpɛ̃mbɔ umɛn nu umɛn ikpɛ̃mɛn abɔɔ.
\p 
\v 4 Bɔr ivangyɛ inna nu ibibemu Unum Uwuku Ufɔrh umɛn iki idzeka,
\v 5 unga afɔrh umɛn, isi iwengge ubin ukpuku urhurhika umɛn iki ikorhe, bɔr awu atorhnga atsu. Unga afɔrh umɛn ru ubok Ipfu Isarsatangge aka asorh arhimmɛn, na adzaa umɛn urhɛ uwuku ufa.
\v 6 Unum awupuwa Ipfu Isarsatangge ru umɛn izũwã ru ubok Uyesu Ukiristo Uwuku Ufɔrh umɛn.
\v 7 Unga anyanga umɛn iwu abika arhika ru ubok imimutanga, ngge itsú umɛn iwe abi ukam urhɛ uwu ugbagbaa umɛn iki ifosa.
\v 8 Akɛrɛ ha awu arherhe idzidzɛrhe. Umum ibee ungo udɛ̃ɛ̃ uker ra abin hã, ngge itsú abirabɛ aka uwe ru imangmang ru Unum adzowe atsimbɔ ri itɔ̃ itser iyiki ize. Abin hã awu azeze na awu ru ugarh ru ubɛn unera.
\p 
\v 9 Bɔr niba utsĩɔ̃ uning uwu ibɛm nu uning anang atokamɛn nu uning aki Ikpem abi Uyahuda, ubinkutsu ashike ru ugarh na asi íyikuke unera.
\v 10 Ugbiite ato uner uning idiki unying nu ide uvaa. Akɛrɛ aba amaake, ugau itsingo nggu unga.
\v 11 Uhwɛng ugɛ ikpũ uner ha aka ayapunga ru utsĩndĩ, anu ikorha arhim, unga aka atsĩmka itsinga.
\s1 Arherhe aka umumasha
\p 
\v 12 Kanying umum ĩba idenukũ Uartima use Utikiku ru ungo, ubee udĩã uba ru umum ru Unikaforhi, ubinkutsu umum iwuri isei umɔ ri ivang ighɛnga.
\v 13 Ubee udĩã uyike Uzena urhoya ha nu Uaforho ru utsĩndĩ nu uhwɛng ugɛ umbɔ akpombɔ ubɛn ubinkpi umbɔ aka abee.
\v 14 Awu ufang anermɛn amesi idzowe atsimbɔ ri ikorhe abin aka aze, nggee umbɔ ama adɛ̃ɛ̃ ayike ifɛr itsũwãmbɔ na niba aseimbɔ isei iyiki isheru ugarh.
\p 
\v 15 Ubɛn unera nggu umum ighwe ungo. Ughwe abika abema umɛn ri imangmang.
\p Imimutu Unum ima iwe nggu umbi kishoo.
